lock-list\">\n<li>Assist students with application forms, SOPs, and other documentation required by universities.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ensure timely submission of applications and act as a point of contact between students and partner universities.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Guide students through the visa application process and coordinate with third-party service providers when needed.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Lead Management:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Follow up on leads generated through various marketing campaigns and convert inquiries into enrollments.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Maintain accurate records of student profiles, applications, and interactions using CRM tools.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Networking &amp; Outreach:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Build and maintain strong relationships with students, parents, educational institutions, and universities.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Represent Eclave at education fairs, webinars, and other events to promote its services.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Conduct workshops and seminars to educate students about study abroad opportunities.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Market Research &amp; Feedback:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Stay updated on global education trends, admission cycles, and changes in visa regulations.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gather feedback from students to enhance counseling services and refine processes.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Skill Set Required<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Counseling Skills:<\/strong> Exceptional ability to connect with students and understand their goals.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Communication Skills:<\/strong> Excellent verbal and written communication in English; proficiency in other languages is a plus.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Organizational Skills:<\/strong> Ability to handle multiple students and applications simultaneously with a high degree of accuracy.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tech Savvy:<\/strong> Proficiency in using CRM software, Microsoft Office, and virtual communication platforms (Zoom, Teams).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Problem-Solving:<\/strong> Strong analytical thinking to address student queries and provide effective solutions.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Interpersonal Skills:<\/strong> Empathetic, patient, and approachable demeanor to build trust and rapport with clients.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Job Requirements<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Educational Qualification:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Bachelor\u2019s degree in Education, Counseling, or a related field.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Certification in Counseling or Student Mentorship is an added advantage.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Experience:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>0\u20133 years of experience in academic counseling, career guidance, or study abroad consulting.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fresh graduates with exceptional communication and mentoring skills are welcome to apply.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Personality Traits:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Passionate about helping students achieve their academic and career aspirations.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Proactive, goal-driven, and adaptable to the dynamic environment of a startup.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Availability:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Willingness to work flexible hours, including weekends, to accommodate student needs.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Openness to travel locally and internationally, if required, for events and partnerships.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Others:<\/strong>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Basic understanding of international education systems, scholarships, and visa processes is preferred.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Why Join Eclave?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Be a part of a mission-driven startup revolutionizing overseas education guidance.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Opportunity to work with students globally and build a meaningful career in the EdTech industry.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Competitive salary, performance-based incentives, and career growth opportunities.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Continuous professional development through training and exposure to global markets.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Join Eclave and make a difference in shaping students\u2019 futures!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Job Title : Study Abroad Counsellor Company: Eclave EdTechLocation: TN, IndiaType: Full-time \/ HybridExperience Level: Entry to Mid-LevelIndustry: EdTech, Overseas<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"template":"","meta":[],"class_list":["post-4035","awsm_job_openings","type-awsm_job_openings","status-publish","hentry","job-category-job"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.9 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Study Abroad Counsellor - Eclave<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/eclave.in\/career\/study-abroad-counsellor\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Study Abroad Counsellor - Eclave\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Job Title : Study Abroad Counsellor Company: Eclave EdTechLocation: TN, IndiaType: Full-time \/ HybridExperience Level: Entry to Mid-LevelIndustry: EdTech, Overseas\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/eclave.in\/career\/study-abroad-counsellor\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Eclave\" \/>\n<meta pr